        is built on recognizing patterns ‚Äî a layout I‚Äôve seen before, a
        structure that worked in the past or a component I‚Äôve used 10 times that
        still works. I‚Äôm mostly not reinventing the wheel, only picking and
        choosing when to reinvent it‚Äîand maybe make it a little prettier.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Q2 -->
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col gap-[24px] text-[14px] font-mr font-semibold"
  >
    <hr />
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[48px]">
