        Nope. I kind of avoid that on purpose. I‚Äôm not trying to inject me into
        every project(sometimes I do). But the goal is mostly to extract the
        essence of the idea, the brand and the people behind it‚Äînot make it look
        like it came out of my personal template. That said, my only ‚Äústyle‚Äù is
        simplicity, intention, and a little edge where it fits. I work hard to
        get to the kind of simplicity that‚Äôs not just minimal, but meaningful.
