          with meüòÇ), ‚ÄúCreativity is just connecting things.‚Äù Looking back at
          some of the things I‚Äôve designed, I realize most of it didn‚Äôt come
          from thin air. It came from noticing things, absorbing them, remixing
          them with intention.</span
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Q7 -->
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col gap-[24px] text-[14px] font-mr font-semibold"
  >
    <hr />
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[48px]">
      <h2 class="text-secondary">
        Q7: How does your coding background influence your design?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-tertiary">
