      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Q11 -->
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col gap-[24px] text-[14px] font-mr font-semibold"
  >
    <hr />
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[48px]">
      <h2 class="text-secondary">
        Q11: What do you value most in collaborators?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-tertiary">
        Honesty. The ability to say "I don‚Äôt think this would work but let‚Äôs
        figure it out." I appreciate working with devs who care about the
        experience, with PMs who respect creative mess, and with founders who
        trust but also challenge. The best work I‚Äôve done came from spaces where
        everyone had a stake and wasn‚Äôt afraid to speak up, learn and challenge
        standard conventions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Q12 -->
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col gap-[24px] text-[14px] font-mr font-semibold"
  >
    <hr />
