  </div>

  <!-- Here‚Äôs how it all comes together -->
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col gap-[24px] text-[14px] font-mr font-semibold"
  >
    <hr />
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[48px]">
      <h2 class="text-secondary">Here‚Äôs how it all comes together</h2>
      <p class="text-tertiary flex flex-col gap-[24px]">
        <span class="block"
          >This mindset‚Äîof thinking in systems, moving between pixels and code,
          and focusing on how things feel and function‚Äîis baked into everything
